    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "If you add a task to a group after canceling the group,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "that task is canceled immediately after being added to the group.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Immediately cancelled child tasks should therefore cooperatively check for and",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "react  to cancellation, e.g. by throwing an ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "CancellationError",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " at their",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "earliest convenience, or otherwise handling the cancellation.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "There are no restrictions on where you can call this method.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Code inside a child task or even another task can cancel a group,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "however one should be very careful to not keep a reference to the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "group longer than the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "with...TaskGroup(...) { ... }",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " method body is executing.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "Task.isCancelled",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
